{
  "stem": "18960.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Then they declared me an official mason.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I mastered the trade.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And that came in very handy to me in my later years during the Nazi occupation.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I was committing-- doing that-- the slave work there till about the fall of 1942.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "During that period of time, there were a lot of [GERMAN], so-called, and the-- they decimated the Jewish population very substantially.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they-- they were deported to the extermination camp, basically to Belzec.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We got wind of it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We found out where they going.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And-- but our group was somehow-- because of our productivity, we were spared and they did not deport us.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But it was about October-- end of October of 1942, my cousin, that-- I before mentioned, engineer Naftali Backenroth, approached me.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And he says, you know, the outlook here is not very good for Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I have a lot of confidence in you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "He meant me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I know somebody that came back from Germany [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] for vacation, for the winter vacation.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "He works in Germany.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And he has a permit to cross the Polish-German border because he has to go back-- back to work there, after the holidays.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I could arrange it-- of course, it'll cost some money-- to buy this permit from him, to use it just for-- for the crossing of the German-Polish border, go to Germany.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And I have confidence in you that you will manage to pull this one and survive the war.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "If you're willing to do it, let me know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I went back home.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I remember at that time, my mother was hiding in the bunker, because of course the [GERMAN] was taking place.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And I went to the bunker.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And I remember her pale face.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
